@NODE Install "Installation"

    Copy this drawer to a place of your harddisk or a disk.

    That's it.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Start "Playing"

    Your goal is to get a line, horizontal, vertical or diagonal with your
    symbol on a field 3x3.

    If you use a PAL-Amiga and don't like the fullscreen display, you can
    run TTT_NTSC (Screen is only 200 lines high).


    @{b}The menu:@{ub}

    @{fg highlight}Start@{fg text}       Start one game

    @{fg highlight}Stop@{fg text}        Stop the current game

    @{fg highlight}Players@{fg text}     Choose 1 or 2 player mode

    @{fg highlight}Names@{fg text}       Type in your name

    @{fg highlight}Quit@{fg text}        ???

@ENDNODE

